data.description: Awesome home located in a private setting on a cul-de-sac with RV parking! This park-like lot is a huge .43 acre with mature landscaping and is close to shopping, medical and a park!  The very inviting and cozy home is 2271 sq ft, with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, kitchen with granite counter tops, a large living area with dining room and family room with gas fireplace. Nicely thought-out floorplan with oak flooring throughout. Freshly painted and carpeted. Out back enjoy sitting by the pond filled with coy fish or a nice walk with family on the walking trail nearby. Included in the backyard is a small shed. This home has it all, a must see!
